dct_title_s: Map of France for statistical division - A.O.O. Services : Services of Supply
dct_description_sm: American Expeditionary Forces ; Made in the Office of D. of C. and F., S.O.U.
Shows August 1918 front, national boundaries, land routes, cities.
France and England divided into base sections (1-6), advance section, and intermediate section.
